snippet.textDisplay:
Such a frustrating game to watch. Atletico score early and then park the bus for 85 mins. Fair play they were extremely well organised and we couldn't break them down.


Referee had a shocker IMO. Fell victim to the atmosphere (which was electric) and gave so many fouls against Liverpool which were clear dives and nothing more.


Liverpool looked a little off the pace, but 1-0 is not a bad result. I fancy our chances going back to Anfield and knocking a couple in to squeeze out the tie - but it will be a close one!
snippet.textOriginal:
